{"id":255344,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-临沂陈克贵报警投案161天，入室行凶镇长扬/","date":"2012-10-07T10:31:11Z","modified":"2012-12-01T08:44:43Z","title":"维权网 | 临沂陈克贵报警投案161天，入室行凶镇长扬言要报仇","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）本网信息员获悉：陈光诚的侄子陈克贵被迫自卫，用菜刀砍伤凌晨翻墙进入他家打砸行凶的带队官员张健后自动报警投案，现被关押在临沂看守所已经</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">161</span><span>天。家人和律师多方打探至今杳无音讯，而痊愈后的张健近日却在多个场合公开扬言要“报仇”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，凌晨带队翻墙入室进入陈光福家打砸行凶的镇长张建不仅没有受到任何的处罚，反而调任沂南县财政局任副局长。在张健住院期间，临沂市和沂南县的多位官员多次亲自前往医院探望，如同对待“英雄”一般。张建受宠若惊气焰更加嚣张，近日，在多处场合公开宣称要“报仇”，扬言绝对不会放过陈光福一家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>东师古周边村民对本网信息员说：“张健凶狠残暴，外号‘阎王’，双堠镇的百姓无人不知，不信你可以随便问问双堠镇任何一个村子的老百姓，只要一说‘阎王镇长’没有人不知道是张建的。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另据了解，沂南县政法委书记兼公安局局长马成连非常反感网友把陈光诚的家乡东师古称做“东尸骨”和“冻死骨”，责令下属对敢有此言的村民严惩不怠。对此，有村民戏称“阎王”长期待的地方能没有“尸骨”吗！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据陈光诚的大哥陈光福透露：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>，在律师的帮助下他通过邮寄方式向临沂市沂南县公安局和双堠镇政府递交了政府信息公开申请书，要求公开“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨</span><span>，沂南县公安局搜查陈光福住宅的事实依据和法律依据”，但陈光福至今还没有收到任何回复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈光福几个月前开始学电脑上微博，注册了新浪微博“临沂陈光福”，因思念牵挂儿子克贵而小心翼翼的发一些博文吐露一个父亲对儿子的牵挂之情，但就是这么一些慎之又慎的言语也是经常刚刚发出去就“无影无踪”了，目前仅存的一些博文让良知的人看了无不心酸愤恨。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>附　</span><span>陈光福新浪微博（临沂陈光福）：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、每逢佳节倍思亲。阿贵投案<span lang=\"EN-US\">156</span>天。政府信息公开申请送达<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>天。（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">21:03</span>分）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、阿贵投案第<span lang=\"EN-US\">139</span>天。政府信息公开申请表寄达逾<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>天。所需信息<span lang=\"EN-US\">: 2012<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">年4</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月27</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">凌晨，沂南县公安局搜查陈光福住宅<span lang=\"EN-US\">的事实依据和法律依据。（<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/2854524404/yC16nE1wb\">9<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月15</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日19:37</span></span></a></span></span></span>来自<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">新浪微博</span></span></a> )</span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、阿贵投案第<span lang=\"EN-US\">138</span>天。沂南威武：······陈克贵，持刀砍伤当地政府干部及工作人员。畏罪潜逃。当地公安机关正抓紧追捕。纠结：时间，地点，原因呢？阿贵呀，既然畏罪潜逃你还报啥警啊！还要数着时间等了三个多小时。你不知道公安很忙吗？（<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/2854524404/yBSgq42QF\">9<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月14</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日21:07</span></span></a></span>来自<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">新浪微博</span></span></a> </span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、阿贵投案<span lang=\"EN-US\">134</span>天。今天分别向沂南公安局和双后镇政府递交了政府信息公开申请表。期望知道<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span>号凌晨沂南县公安局和双后镇政 府非法侵入住宅，非法搜查非法侵害的事实依据和法律依据。（<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/2854524404/yBfLfrE6w\">9<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月10</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日19:06</span></span></a></span>来自<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">新浪微博</span></span></a></span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>、阿贵投案第<span lang=\"EN-US\">133</span>天。两年前的今天，被故意毁坏财物的盲弟出狱回家。从此开始了·······（<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/2854524404/yB1fd0dXm\">9<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月9</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日06:08</span></span></a></span>来自<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">新浪微博</span></span></a></span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>、想起两年前的今天。村里增加了诸多陌生面孔，所有进村的路口都有<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>到<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>人<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>小时值守。粗略计算有<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>多人。预示着将有重大事情发生。后来人们把这些人叫看守。（<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/2854524404/yAOOkAnUK\">9<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月7</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日22:29</span></span></a></span>来自<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">新浪微博</span></span></a></span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>、 今天发的两条微博都很快就被加密了，动作好快（<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/2854524404/yAEyVCrLo\">9<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月6</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日20:24</span></span></a></span>来自<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">新浪微博</span></span></a> </span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span>号我和贵妈妈的身份证被抢走，百般索要未果。<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span>号去派出所申请补办，当时交了<span lang=\"EN-US\">124</span>块钱。答复<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>天能收到，<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>天的约定到了吗？我的身份证在哪？（<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/2854524404/yyZlLjHIe\">8<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月26</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日21:38</span></span></a></span>来自<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">新浪微博</span></span></a></span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>、检查院吴女士问：你们请律师了吗？我说请了上海的斯伟江和北京的丁锡奎两位律师，但介入不了，他们给指定了两名法律援助律师。回答这我们不知道。现在应（<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/2854524404/yyAMsq3gN\">8<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月24</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日07:05</span></span></a></span>来自<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">新浪微博</span></span></a> </span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>、刚才去检查院询问阿贵的案子到了没有？吴姓便装女士告诉我：没有收到这个案子。 确实没收到？确实没收到。都<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>个月了怎么会没收到呢？真的没收到。（<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/2854524404/yysSqeYGZ\">8<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月23</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日10:58</span></span></a></span>来自<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://weibo.com/\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">新浪微博</span></span></a> </span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7752660832052779362?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\